  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\">\n<div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:402px;\">\n<div style=\"position: relative; border: 1px solid lightgray\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Location_map_Known_world.svg\" class=\"image\" title=\"Asabhad is located in The Known World\"><img alt=\"Asabhad is located in The Known World\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/69/Location_map_Known_world.svg/400px-Location_map_Known_world.svg.png\" width=\"400\" height=\"267\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/69/Location_map_Known_world.svg/600px-Location_map_Known_world.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/69/Location_map_Known_world.svg/800px-Location_map_Known_world.svg.png 2x\" /></a><div style=\"position: absolute; z-index: 2; top: 73.7%; left: 75.7%; height: 0; width: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"><div style=\"position: relative; text-align: center; left: -4px; top: -4px; width: 8px; font-size: 8px; z-index:100;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/8px-Red_pog.png\" title=\"Asabhad\" width=\"8\" height=\"8\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/12px-Red_pog.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/16px-Red_pog.png 2x\" /></div><div style=\"font-size:&#160;%; line-height: 110%; z-index:90; position: relative; top: -1.5em; width: 6em; top:-2.65em; left:-3em; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"padding: 1px;\">Asabhad</span></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"thumbcaption\">Location of Asabhad in the <a href=\"/index.php/Known_world\" title=\"Known world\">known world</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p><b>Asabhad</b> is a city at the western boundary of <a href=\"/index.php/Yi_Ti\" title=\"Yi Ti\">Yi Ti</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiafasabhad.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiafasabhad.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> in <a href=\"/index.php/Essos\" title=\"Essos\">Essos</a> along the shores of the <a href=\"/index.php/Jade_Sea\" title=\"Jade Sea\">Jade Sea</a>, east of the <a href=\"/index.php/Bone_Mountains\" title=\"Bone Mountains\">Bone Mountains</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtloiafthe_known_world.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtloiafthe_known_world.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> It is located at a forested river mouth.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtloiafthe_known_world.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtloiafthe_known_world.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> Situated on a trade route connecting <a href=\"/index.php/Qarth\" title=\"Qarth\">Qarth</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Yin\" title=\"Yin\">Yin</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtloiafthe_east.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtloiafthe_east.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> Asabhad is where many caravans begin their journey to the <a href=\"/index.php/Mountains_of_the_Morn\" title=\"Mountains of the Morn\">Mountains of the Morn</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiafasabhad.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiafasabhad.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Asabhad&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rawoiafasabhad.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rawoiafasabhad.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rawoiafasabhad.7B.7B.7B